data.description: Check out this large and well maintained 3 bedrooms and 2 bath unit with an eat-in kitchen combo.  Many updates and improvements were done in 2016 throughout the unit; new flooring, both bathrooms were updated and newer kitchen. This unit is move in ready. Walking distance to public transportation, restaurant, bank, recreation, Forest Park shopping strip and downtown Oak Park. Just minutes to I290. Seller will pay first 6 months of assessments.
